metadata.name: Doom Scroll #1
metadata.description: Doom Scrolls are blockchain prophecies, divined by an evil Tubby Cat, brewed with powdered wolfsbane and the body of a Wassie (diced). Fully on-chain, immutable, visions of your demise. Death is the utility, beware!!

attributes.value: stalked by a drone 300 feet above
body will be stuffed in a trunk and driven into the river
as you're remembered fondly by all
